org.hibernate.ogm.query.impl

Class NoSQLQueryImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.internal.AbstractQueryImpl
      • org.hibernate.ogm.query.impl.NoSQLQueryImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BasicQueryContract, NoSQLQuery, Query, SQLQuery, SynchronizeableQuery

    public class NoSQLQueryImpl
extends AbstractQueryImpl
implements NoSQLQuery
    Hibernate OGM implementation of the SQLQuery contract.

    This class is a copy of SQLQueryImpl and it is needed because the constructors in of SQlQueryImpl are package-private and they cannot be called when our application is deployed on WildFly.

    It also has a better name for a class dealing with NoSQL databases.

    Author:
    Davide D'Alto <davide@hibernate.org>
